{"tid":1302574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文憑試超級狀元反中亂港?","createTime":"2019-07-10T03:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T04:23:08.000Z","uid":160075,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a6aac6f6e58f5c65905db1e2895a6fbbd738f8","tid":1302574,"uid":160075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"2019年中學文憑試今日放榜，今年共誕生12名考獲七科5**狀元，五男一女更在數學延伸部分取得5**成為「超級狀元」。其中聖保羅男女中學的「超級狀元」甘浚祺對今次成績感到意外和驚喜，原定目標只是希望夠分入讀醫科，因為他小學五年班曾經患上急性白血病，在公立醫院接受整整一年的治療，希望成為醫生幫助更多病童。<br />\n<br />\n甘浚祺在小四至小五時曾患急性林巴白血病，經醫護人員悉心照料，自小立志成為醫生而打算讀醫，暫未決定入讀哪所大學。他本身來自中層家庭，爸爸任職會計，媽媽則是家庭主婦，年少時家人對他的功課也有催谷，但自從患病後改變了家人看法，給予他很大的自由。<br />\n<br />\n提到最近社會爭議，甘浚祺認為外界應了解持不同立場的人，背後所思所想，他自己曾參加六月十九日的反修例遊行，有機會再遊行表達，又認為通識教育科有助學生思考，積極回應社會議題。他表示，社會氣氛有影響情緒，出現無力和無奈感，但他不認同有人指是通識科引發一連串示威活動，反而覺得通識科令學生更關注社會。<br />\n<br />\n提到讀書心得，他形容是以平常心應付，但溫習過程亦曾失去信心與動力，他自己就會打機減壓<br />\n<br />\n資料來源: <a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1040876-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90DSE%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E6%82%A3%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%80%E7%97%85+%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%8B%80%E5%85%83%E3%80%8D%E8%AE%80%E9%86%AB%E5%86%80%E5%8A%A9%E7%97%85%E7%AB%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1040876-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590DSE%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A6%259C%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2582%25A3%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%2580%25E7%2597%2585%2B%25E8%2581%2596%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25BE%2585%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%258B%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25AE%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2597%2585%25E7%25AB%25A5&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=e686721f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1040876-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590DSE%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A6%259C%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2582%25A3%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%2580%25E7%2597%2585%2B%25E8%2581%2596%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25BE%2585%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%258B%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25AE%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2597%2585%25E7%25AB%25A5&h=ef2a91c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1040876-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90DSE%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E6%82%A3%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%80%E7%97%85+%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%8B%80%E5%85%83%E3%80%8D%E8%AE%80%E9%86%AB%E5%86%80%E5%8A%A9%E7%97%85%E7%AB%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甘同學，你貴為狀元仲反中亂港，你係咪中國人? 定係美國派黎既間諜 。以你既級數，你究竟收左幾多錢去遊行?  遊行係班廢青比人洗左腦或者係收左錢先會去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你搞串左個party啦 依加班藍絲點駁好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefffa50f70de53e680a189b1628a9e5238b882d","tid":1302574,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"廢老又會話你讀屎片, 冇Critical Thinking"},{"pid":"30f5f9811372dd5f7bf84cb88980d84fd248c211","tid":1302574,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"藍絲子女繼續讀毅進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9d74640a2561593351e3f21ff51b56fac1f248","tid":1302574,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"7.10 - TVB港姐 - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n7.10 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=9af50170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br /